            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am studying in this school right now and I don't think so anything is good about this school..the headmistress don't even solve the case .... most of the teachers r rude... no games r played during pe period ... lot of fees is charged.. so many rules and regulations r there just for students. Teacher wards get so much privilege and they score good marks .I just wish to get out of this school asap ... the teacher wards r allowed to meet their parents but others r not ... if a teacher ward is travelling in bus ,, no fees is charged frim them .... and the councillor such as shangrila mam will never be helping u in any case ..... worst school",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
