            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Study system is very good but teachers are very bad everyday they keep exams they talk rudely to the parents I studied till 10th except 6th 7th 8th teachers were not that bad but 6,7,8 teachers had pathetic behaviour my parents somehow stopped me leaving the school in 8th but in 10th I couldn't bare it I immediately left the school their teachers abuse also If teachers had a good behaviour this could have been a good my suggestions\nAre to expel ms kamaljeet Kaur",
          "publisher": {
