          },
          "datePublished": "2024-10-15",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I recently had the pleasure of going on a trip with DPS Chandigarh to Jaipur, and it was truly a wonderful experience. The children were incredibly sweet and respectful, and I learned so much from them. But the teachers were beyond words—despite being tired, they still found ways to lift our spirits and always on their toes to help. Their care and dedication reminded me of the nurturing presence of a mother. I feel so grateful and honored to have been their journey mentor.\n\nTeachers were\nMs Neha,Ms Arpana, Mr Mani,Ms Diksha, Ms Preeti,Ms Kanchan ,Mr Raghav",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
